		{
			dependencies: ["67A5093E7141315C"]
			description: [
				"The &bMatter Cannon&r is a weapon that can be used to &6fire a variety of items&r at your adversaries:"
				""
				"- Various nuggets"
				"- Matter and Paint Balls"
				""
				"The damage is dictated &bby the material&r itself, so a Uranium Nugget will deal much more damage than a Matter Ball."
				""
				"Charge this weapon using a Charger or other means."
				""
				"In order to load the Cannon with ammo, it can be &bused as a Storage Cell&r. Ideally, you'll want to use an &6ME Chest&r for this."
				""
				"The Cannon also supports a variety of &bupgrade cards&r, which can be applied with a&6 Cell Workbench&r."
			]
			id: "4965B2003FAFC7F5"
			min_width: 250
			rewards: [{
				id: "2122B0172CCBD3AD"
