		}
		{
			dependencies: ["67A5093E7141315C"]
			description: [
				"The &bColor Applicator&r is a handy tool if you need to &6recolor blocks&r such as &bcables&r, terracotta, wool, and concrete."
				""
				"It can take &6Paint Balls and Dyes&r as ammo for recoloring blocks, and &6Snowballs&r can be used to remove colors off cables and paintball splotches left by a Matter Cannon."
				""
				"Like the Matter Cannon, this item &bfunctions as a Storage Cell&r, and can be filled with ammo ideally with an &6ME Chest&r."
				""
				"It must also be charged with power via a Charger or other means."
			]
			id: "04B6F3DB7402B007"
			min_width: 250
			rewards: [{
