		{
			dependencies: ["67A5093E7141315C"]
			description: [
				"The &bNetwork Tool&r is useful when dealing with networks, as it can &6display diagnostic information&r about a network on use, such as connected devices. "
				""
				"Like the wrench used to craft it, it can also &6easily remove cables and subparts&r individually, but it can no longer rotate blocks."
				""
				"The Tool can also be used in the air to open its own inventory, where you can put &bup to 9 stacks of upgrade cards&r, which will be accessible in most AE2 UIs."
			]
			id: "0E2995DC87230012"
			rewards: [{
				id: "72B3E7E79722D3FA"
				type: "xp"
				xp: 20
			}]
			subtitle: "The 64th wrench you'll ever need!"
