		}
		{
			dependencies: ["67A5093E7141315C"]
			description: [
				"The &bME Chest&r can be used either as a network device, or on its own. It acts as a &6Terminal and a single Storage Cell slot&r in one block."
				""
				"This can be useful for &6refilling certain tools&r with items, such as the &bMatter Cannon and Color Applicator&r."
				""
				"If &6attached to a Network&r, the Chest's Terminal can only access the contents of the Storage Cell &6contained inside it&r, which could potentially be useful in some cases."
			]
			id: "59C800B2D13FF5AA"
			rewards: [{
