		}
		{
			dependencies: ["67A5093E7141315C"]
			description: [
				"The &6Matter Condenser&r is a &btrash can&r by default. However, it also has a &bcouple other modes&r. Note that the Condenser can take &6both items and fluids&r."
				""
				"By supplying it with at least a &61k ME Storage Component&r and selecting the &6correct mode&r, every &b256 items&r thrown into it will create &b1 Matter Ball&r."
				""
				"In &cPhase III&r, if supplied with at least a &664k ME Storage Component&r and in the correct mode, every &b256,000 items&r will create &b1 Singularity&r."
			]
